text: The 2016 German Figure Skating Championships () was held on December 11-13, 2015 at the Eissporthalle Essen West in Essen. Skaters competed in the disciplines of men's singles, ladies' singles, pair skating, and ice dancing on the senior, junior, and novice levels.
